title: Top 10 RB Rankings + Austin Ekeler Joins the Show! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/9
description:
On today’s fantasy football podcast, running back rankings for 2022! Do you dare take CMC with the top draft pick? Is Alvin Kamara worth the suspension risk? What could go wrong for the elite RBs? Plus, a fun interview with Chargers RB Austin Ekeler! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 9th, 2022
